{"title":"火热的三峡（组诗）","authors":["唐刚"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":11,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"火热的三峡（组诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐刚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从重庆到宜昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从重庆到宜昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路江风一路激浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三天三夜在江轮上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我发现夹岸峭壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像老人向我讲述着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三峡岁月和历史的沧桑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船过巫峡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望神女峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神女神采飘扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在云雾缭绕中向游人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展示爱的地久天长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船过秭归"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香溪的水就飘来芳香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚回过神船已抵达"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三峡建设工地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时天色将晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工地上灯火辉煌犹似"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九天撒落一地星光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仔细搜寻记忆中的中堡岛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我凝目注视这举世瞩目的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工地夜景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊我听见滚滚长江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这根中国巨大的弦上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正被三峡建设者们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用双手夜以继日地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹奏出时代的最高乐章……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这座古老的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴城被三峡建设者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用大手将它搬上了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半山腰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴城变成了新巴城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车辆犹如"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长龙摆阵从江岸到山腰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正满载着搬迁的物资"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在通往新巴城的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大道上驰骋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴城人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬进了新家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些年轻的移民的脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎有一朵朵微笑盛开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而那些年老的爷爷奶奶脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却似乎有一丝丝愁云……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位刚搬进新居的大娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有些依依不舍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像出嫁的闺女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离开娘亲……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦巴城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可听见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是巴城人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对故园难离难舍的心声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火热的工地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吊塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吊起了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天的朝云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火热的工地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像一个战场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人与坚固的岩石战斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与巨大的江流战斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与各色各样的困难战斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要用自己的双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"描绘出三峡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最新的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工地上我看见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那位工程师兼指挥长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已有两年没回他的北京老家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那位开塔吊的小伙子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里一干就是五年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年中他的父母多次来信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催他回家办婚事他总是说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还早还早嘞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等到大江截流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他就回家成亲……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵火热的三峡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火热的工地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像一个巨大的“陷阱”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要你一旦陷进去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就会变成它的“俘虏”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的情人……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江截流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江请你记住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三峡请你记住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公元１９９７年１１月８日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这天大江截流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江截流就是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"截住长江千年洪汛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江截流就是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积蓄长江明天的温柔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"截流这是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何等的壮举呀全世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万双的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都大睁着等候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一天终于来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三峡建设者这些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大禹的后代们仅用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一千八百多个日日夜夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就将长江这条巨龙降服"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此造福人类"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让滚滚洪流变得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温温顺顺碧波悠悠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵截流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华民族近百年的梦想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终将成为巍峨的现实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——高峡平湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展示世纪风流……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}